headline: IVZ Among Top-Performing S&P 500 Asset Managers in 2025: Is It a Buy?
summary: Invesco soars 53.5% in 2025, topping S&P 500 asset managers. However, muted revenue growth and high intangibles raise buy-or-wait questions.
